ory";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:26:"WordPress Portfolio Plugin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:36:"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=2817";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:409:"Product: WonderPlugin Portfolio Plugin Question: I use Wistia to house video I wonder how to show the video in lightbox popup. Answer: In the plugin, step 1, Click Add Image button: Select an image for the grid Uncheck the option &#8230; <a href="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-portfolio-plugin/how-to-display-wistia-video-in-lightbox-popup/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"WonderPlugin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1275:"<p><strong>Product</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-gridgallery/" target="_blank">WonderPlugin Portfolio Plugin</a></p>\n<p><strong>Question</strong>:</p>\n<p>I use Wistia to house video I wonder how to show the video in lightbox popup.</p>\n<p><strong>Answer</strong>:</p>\n<p>In the plugin, step 1, Click Add Image button:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Select an image for the grid</li>\n<li>Uncheck the option "Open current image in lightbox" then enter the Wistia iframe URL to the "click to open web link" field.</li>\n<li>Check the option "open web link in lightbox"</li>\n<li>You can also check the option "Set Lightbox Size"</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/wistia-lightbox.png" class="wplightbox"><img src="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/wistia-lightbox-600x598.png" alt="wistia lightbox gallery" width="600" height="598" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2818" srcset="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/wistia-lightbox-600x598.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/wistia-lightbox-301x300.png 301w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/wistia-lightbox.png 773w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:33:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:3:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:71:"Display SoundCloud in the Lightbox Popup of WordPress Portfolio Gallery";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:128:"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-portfolio-plugin/display-soundcloud-in-the-lightbox-popup-of-wordpress-portfolio-gallery/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 05 Oct 2015 01:30:56 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:26:"WordPress Portfolio Plugin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:36:"https://www.wonderplugin.com/?p=2805";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:456:"Product: WonderPlugin Portfolio Grid Gallery Question: Is there any way to display SoundCloud in the lightbox popup? Answer: 1. Goto Soundcloud, the music, click Share button, then click Embed tab, copy the src value from the provided iframe code. Do &#8230; <a href="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-portfolio-plugin/display-soundcloud-in-the-lightbox-popup-of-wordpress-portfolio-gallery/">Continue reading <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"WonderPlugin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2204:"<p><strong>Product:</strong></p>\n<p><a href="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-gridgallery/" target="_blank">WonderPlugin Portfolio Grid Gallery</a></p>\n<p><strong>Question:</strong></p>\n<p>Is there any way to display SoundCloud in the lightbox popup?</p>\n<p><strong>Answer:</strong></p>\n<p>1. Goto Soundcloud, the music, click Share button, then click Embed tab, copy the src value from the provided iframe code.</p>\n<p><strong>Do not use the whole iframe code, only copy the value of the src value.</strong></p>\n<p><a href="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/soundcloud-embed.png" class="wplightbox"><img src="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/soundcloud-embed-600x421.png" alt="soundcloud-embed" width="600" height="421" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2808" srcset="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/soundcloud-embed-240x168.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/soundcloud-embed-600x421.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/soundcloud-embed-428x300.png 428w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/soundcloud-embed.png 712w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></a></p>\n<p>2. In WonderPlugin Portfolio Grid Gallery, Add/Edit Image dialog, enter the src value to the "Click to open web link" text box, check the option "Open web link in lightbox". You can also check the option "Set Lightbox Size".</p>\n<p><a href="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/soundcloud-lightbox.png" class="wplightbox"><img src="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/soundcloud-lightbox-600x348.png" alt="SoundCloud Lightbox Gallery" width="600" height="348" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2809" srcset="https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/soundcloud-lightbox-240x139.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/soundcloud-lightbox-600x348.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/soundcloud-lightbox-500x290.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/soundcloud-lightbox.png 851w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:33:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:3:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:61:"Link to Pages or Posts in WonderPlugin Portfolio Grid Gallery";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:118:"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-portfolio-plugin/link-to-pages-or-posts-in-wonderplugin-portfolio-grid-gallery/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Sun, 20 Sep 2015 11:07:12 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:26:"WordPress Portfolio Plugin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"